Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:25.37,default - cyan - with - background,,0,0,0,,あいつがまた帰ってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:25.37,Default - white - with - background,,0,0,0,,He's come back again
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.05,0:04:26.91,Default - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(757.459,391.064)}Igawa Hiroyuki
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:26.91,Default - red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(778,634)}Furukawa Yuki
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.42,0:04:31.55,default - cyan - with - background,,0,0,0,,ざわざわと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.42,0:04:31.55,Default - white - with - background,,0,0,0,,In anxiety...
