Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.78,0:04:35.58,Default - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(783.195,757.39)}Akagi Shigeru
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:42.57,default - cyan - with - background,,0,0,0,,誰の肩に止まるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:42.57,Default - white - with - background,,0,0,0,,Whose shoulder will it land upon
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:48.57,default - cyan - with - background,,0,0,0,,くるくる廻る天道虫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:48.57,Default - white - with - background,,0,0,0,,Ladybug going round and round
