Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.75,0:05:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(628,434)}Ten: Tenho-doori no Kaidanji\N(The Nice Guy on Tenho Way)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.75,0:05:10.08,Default - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(642,606)}Episode 1
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.84,0:05:05.11,default - cyan - with - background,,0,0,0,,陽が昇った
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.84,0:05:05.11,Default - white - with - background,,0,0,0,,The sun rose
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.41,0:05:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So, a wager between you and I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.65,0:05:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm confident anything will be fine .Only...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do a side bet
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Side bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.45,0:05:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If I win, you give back what you won from everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need any money
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I double your winnings
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a ringer, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.28,0:05:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been wanting to meet someone like you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,As I haven't yet beenbeaten in Mahjong,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I could become a ringer myself
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then it's decided
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.14,0:05:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,At the table over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A non-automatic table must be so he can cheat
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's got to be it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.62,0:06:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If he didn't do that he couldn't be sure to beat someone he doesn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.34,0:06:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand stacking tiles isn't a problem is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:27.31,Default - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1086.792,576)}East Round 1
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.51,0:06:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The contest is one East South round, and whoever has more points wins, even if its merely 100 more
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.65,0:06:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,First I have to make sure there's no cheating
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.65,0:06:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do a single wait on an undiscarded tile, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll apply some pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,12,000 points
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.41,0:07:40.71,Default - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1071.698,582)}South Round 1
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.77,0:07:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,8,000 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this character? The silent type
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:10.45,Default - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1068.679,576)}South Round 2
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.98,0:08:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.95,0:08:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,12,000 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,0:08:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a novice wouldn't deal into that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.17,0:08:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All that remains is this guy's turn as dealer
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.42,0:08:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm in the lead by 50,000 points
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.68,0:08:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what is he playing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.11,0:09:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell happened? A blackout?\NTurn on the lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.74,0:09:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,S-sorry. I hit the switch with my elbow
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.14,0:09:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten. It's your turn
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.55,0:09:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. I got this
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,*Tenhou Chuuren PouTou
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:33.05,Default - top - cyan,,0,0,0,,*{\b1}Chuuren PouTou{\b0}(九連宝燈) Special Yakuman (high scoring hand) "The Nine gates" \N* {\b1}Tenhou{\b0} (天和): Dealer completes hand on first tile draw
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.17,0:09:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.78,0:09:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Typical Ten. It's a complete reversal of 90,000 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.17,0:09:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not possible! You cheated!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you admit it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.22,0:09:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:10:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mahjong
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,is a truly fearsome thing isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.71,0:10:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hold on a second.\NAdmit you cheated
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,When you arranged your hand the tile wall in front of you moved a tiny amount
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.14,0:10:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow or other it was a brilliant trick of the tiles
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.14,0:10:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you, a pro, embarrassed to do something so childish?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A sneaky underworld guy like you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.85,0:10:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I could become a ringer right now
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.68,0:10:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh\NDon't make me laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.85,0:10:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:10:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Name
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Igawa Hiroyuki
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiroyuki, hunh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Being a ringer...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.28,0:11:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is the business of shouldering the burden of other people's lives
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,People bet more than their lives
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.71,0:11:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether by guile or cheating outright
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.34,0:11:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to win by any means necessary
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you happy to win such a low victory?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.97,0:11:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be content playing the Mahjong of a charlatan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is being a Pro
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's regrettable but,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.81,0:11:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the sweet world you imagine is very far from the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I got no use for you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.17,0:12:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I watched your Mahjong very closely
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.11,0:12:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In that match, Ten did cheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.51,0:12:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You won.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.41,0:12:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Your ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you test it once more?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.55,0:12:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Sawada! Come in, come in
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our ringer for the game
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.30,0:12:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ringer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.31,0:12:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, he's a young one
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got the chops
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.18,0:12:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in real estate
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.75,0:12:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me Maruo
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.75,0:12:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Igawa
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.47,0:12:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, this is about a deed
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:12:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and you'll play Mahjong for it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.71,0:13:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,a deed for a... plot of land?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm looking to get his fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.58,0:13:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I already own half of his home and property by gambling and debt
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.21,0:13:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And the remaining half,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.67,0:13:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,will be dealt with by Mahjong
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawada found you for your strength in Mahjong
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, this is Maruo
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.01,0:13:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,These guys are pure trash, but they're the most powerful gang right now
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to take shelter where we can
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.38,0:13:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it means protecting garbage like that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.65,0:13:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But in such an important deal can I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there. I KNOW
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen a lot of ringers before now
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.07,0:13:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hiding an ability far beyond that crowd
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.38,0:13:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Have confidence in your own Mahjong
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm betting on you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.08,0:14:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Being a ringer,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.30,0:14:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the business of shouldering the burden of other people's lives
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I got no use for you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.81,0:14:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Igawa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,After you take his shop, how about a victory celebration?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.91,0:14:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your mind on the game
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.81,0:14:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.67,0:14:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakanishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.38,0:14:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you bring the deed like a good boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.18,0:15:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.18,0:15:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.21,0:15:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I've wanted to see a contest against you one more time
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And this time I won't lose
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.32,0:15:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever your cheats
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.49,0:15:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The contest is 5 East South rounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:15:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The winner is the first to take 3 rounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.33,0:16:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.59,0:16:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Me and Hiroyuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,make the game the difference between our points.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.56,0:16:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. It's no problem
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then. It's decided
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.06,0:16:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten. Just what are you plotting?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.93,0:16:37.16,Default - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(223.396,519)}First Game\NEast Round One
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.93,0:16:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In this situation, Ten can't possibly cheat
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.66,0:16:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I ought to be vigilant against anything he does
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.03,0:16:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But this Nakanishi guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.60,0:17:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Chii
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A Man (character tile) single suit hand, hunh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.63,0:17:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you've already got enough of them
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.43,0:17:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not in Tenpai
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.18,0:17:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not in Tenpai
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:08.73,Default - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1104.906,525)}First Game\NEast Round 3
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.69,0:18:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This time he's collecting Pin (dot) tiles
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.49,0:19:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Discarding the Dora tile after he drew it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.23,0:19:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He couldn't make such dangerous discards from a worthless hand so often
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.09,0:19:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought. He's about to win
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.09,0:19:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't discard Pin tiles
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.66,0:19:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can't discard from this meld near the Dora
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:20:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.46,0:20:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.19,0:20:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,7,700 points
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What a shit break
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.76,0:20:22.19,Default - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(187.17,525)}First Game\NSouth Round 4
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.38,0:20:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.72,0:21:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He discarded the Dora within one turn of Sawada's Riichi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ordinarily no one would consider discarding that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.86,0:21:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakanishi's certainly got a single suit hand
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.63,0:21:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.76,0:21:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,2,000 points
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.72,0:22:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you play so sluggishly, you'll lose
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.29,0:22:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He's confusing you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.63,0:22:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What you don't know is scaring you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.49,0:22:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.49,0:22:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.28,0:22:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a ringer because my dead mom left this place to me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.23,0:22:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,PLEASE!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.13,0:22:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it since I owe you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.26,0:22:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You've led an honest, straightforward life...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.55,0:22:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you gamble it all away?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.76,0:22:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically I was tricked
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.86,0:22:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I was cheated out of everything in a light game of poker
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.49,0:22:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I noticed they had half my shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.26,0:22:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.26,0:22:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All things considered, you just can't beat them
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.26,0:22:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,PLEASE!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.26,0:22:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Please save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.76,0:22:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten. I'm pleading with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.89,0:23:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.23,0:23:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you become a {\b1\i1}heretic{\b0\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.32,0:23:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A... heretic?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.15,0:23:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Up to now you've led an honest, straightforward life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.46,0:23:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's no good for this contest
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.36,0:23:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This shop, your land...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.29,0:23:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want them to be stolen
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.35,0:23:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,become a heretical, UNORTHODOX player for me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.92,0:23:50.09,Default - top,,0,0,0,,Ten knows Nakanishi has been faking single suit hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.09,0:23:53.32,Default - top,,0,0,0,,it's all been a bluff
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.59,0:23:56.59,Default - top,,0,0,0,,Only,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.59,0:24:00.00,Default - top,,0,0,0,,They've put his shop on the line
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.00,0:24:02.00,Default - top,,0,0,0,,Nakanishi...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.00,0:24:05.26,Default - top,,0,0,0,,It's a bluff burned into his soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.26,0:24:07.40,Default - top,,0,0,0,,And when you carry something like that this far
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.40,0:24:12.26,Default - top,,0,0,0,,It's not a matter of catching people in tricks or anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.26,0:24:15.38,Default - top,,0,0,0,,I'd call it more "divine"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.38,0:24:17.38,Default - top,,0,0,0,,A direct attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.38,0:24:20.46,Default - top,,0,0,0,,you might call it "madness"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.46,0:24:22.98,Default - top,,0,0,0,,They're willing to lose it all
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.93,0:24:28.78,Default - top,,0,0,0,,I don't know what we do next
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.71,0:25:09.31,Default - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(172,156)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.20,0:24:50.96,Default - top,,0,0,0,,Well then. Round two
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.06,0:24:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.68,0:24:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,People can obtain what they desire through HOPE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.33,0:25:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,BUT IN GAMBLING IT'S JUST THE OPPOSITE
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.60,0:25:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't end for me like this
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.59,0:25:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.33,0:25:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How did he read my discards?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.98,0:25:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Mahjong level I'm at
